---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';

const locale = 'en';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Careers - KILC"
  description="Join Keane International Legal Consultancy. Current openings for Student Brand Ambassadors and Newly Qualified Solicitors."
>
  <Hero
    title="Careers"
    subtitle="Join our team and make a difference in international legal consultancy."
    backgroundImage="/images/services/career.jpg"
    locale={locale}
  />

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          At KILC, we are building a team of dedicated professionals who are passionate about helping international individuals and businesses navigate the UK legal landscape. We value diverse perspectives, cross-cultural understanding, and a commitment to delivering exceptional client service. If you share our mission, we would love to hear from you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Job Listings -->
      <div class="space-y-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Student Brand Ambassadors -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-sans font-bold text-brand-dark">
              Student Brand Ambassadors
            </h3>
            <span class="inline-block bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
              Part-time
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
              UK Universities
            </span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              Part-time / Flexible
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            We are looking for enthusiastic and well-connected university students to represent KILC on campus. As a Student Brand Ambassador, you will help raise awareness of our services among the international student community, organise events, and serve as a bridge between KILC and students who may benefit from our support. This is an excellent opportunity to gain professional experience, develop your network, and contribute to a meaningful mission.
          </p>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-3">Requirements:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 text-sm mb-6">
            {[
              'Currently enrolled at a UK university',
              'Strong communication and interpersonal skills',
              'Active involvement in student communities',
              'Interest in legal services, immigration, or international affairs',
              'Fluency in English and Mandarin preferred',
            ].map((req) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                {req}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Newly Qualified Solicitors -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-sans font-bold text-brand-dark">
              Newly Qualified Solicitors
            </h3>
            <span class="inline-block bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
              Full-time
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
              London / Hybrid
            </span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              Full-time
            </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            We are seeking ambitious, newly qualified solicitors to join our growing team. You will work across a range of practice areas including immigration, corporate, and commercial law — supporting international clients with their UK legal needs. This role offers significant responsibility from day one and the opportunity to build expertise in cross-border legal matters.
          </p>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-3">Requirements:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 text-sm mb-6">
            {[
              'Qualified solicitor (SQE or LPC route)',
              'Strong academic record',
              'Genuine interest in international and cross-border legal work',
              'Excellent written and verbal communication skills',
              'Mandarin language skills desirable but not essential',
            ].map((req) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                {req}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Apply Section -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 text-center">
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-lg p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-sans font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">
            How to Apply
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            To apply for any of the above positions, please send your CV and a brief covering letter to:
          </p>
          <a
            href="mailto:careers@kilc.co.uk"
            class="inline-block text-xl font-semibold text-brand-primary hover:text-brand-secondary transition-colors"
          >
            careers@kilc.co.uk
          </a>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-4">
            We review all applications carefully and will respond to shortlisted candidates within two weeks.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
